-  5,400 Platinum
-  Arcslayer Cosmetic Armour Set
     -  Arcslayer Helmet
     -  Arcslayer Gauntlets
     -  Arcslayer Jacket
     -  Arcslayer Greaves
-  Arcslayer Torch Lantern Skin
